Monitor soil moisture

Update secrets.py as approrpiate for local configuration specifics.

In code.py, user should set
	NTP_SERVER
		Set to None to not pass a timestamp in measurements, set to a NTP server
		IP/hostname to set RTC to NTP and use local clock time in messages
	QUERY_INT
		Set to number of seconds between queries of the probes
	MQTT_PUB
		Set to True to publish to MQTT broker